SELECT s.name, c.name AS course_name, g.grade FROM students s JOIN enrollments e ON s.student_id = e.student_id JOIN courses c ON e.course_id = c.course_id JOIN grades g ON e.enrollment_id = g.enrollment_id WHERE s.age >= 20 GROUP BY s.name, c.name HAVING AVG(g.grade) > 80;
